uploadId.description: Upload ID assigned when initiating multi-part upload for AWS S3. Obtained from the `/upload` endpoint response.

tags.description: Array of ETags assigned for each part by AWS S3 during the upload process. Each ETag is returned in the response headers when uploading a part to the pre-signed URLs from the `/upload` endpoint.

withError.description: Flag indicating whether the upload encountered an error. If `true`, the upload will be aborted. If `false`, the upload will be completed.
